elements.name: Verify user can make a payment after login to the system.

steps.name: User go to the Prequalification page and select user as "Test User5"
User click on Consent checkbox with value is "Y"
User input on Spend money text box with value is "500000"
User input on Down payment money text box with value is "400000"
User input on Gross income text box with value is "80000"
User input on Monthly Expenses text box with value is "1500"
User should see the Summary Review Page
User click on the Submit button
User should see the Congratulations page
User should see the Congratulations message as "You have qualified for our Mortgage Prequalification Program."

arguments.val: "You have qualified for our Mortgage Prequalification Program."
